body:
today is d's birthday <3 

it has been a hard year for her, but things are so much better than they were and i'm proud of how much work she's done

our relationship is stronger than ever

giving her navigation directions while she's driving

we like the new city where we live

met friends for korean barbecue

one more day of work till vacation

haribo sour cubes gummies

ice, air conditioning, and cool breezes
